"It's our tenth year, let's keep going."

6
00:00:24,557 --> 00:00:28,795
{\an8}<i>Nine years since their debut,
the four stood on a new starting line.</i>

7
00:00:29,996 --> 00:00:33,500
{\an8}<i>There's someone
