memorable in the ten years.

24
00:02:04,557 --> 00:02:06,860
I was always anxious.

25
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:11,297
There was a lot of conflict too, yeah.

26
00:02:12,599 --> 00:02:13,933
I guess it's just...

27
00:02:15,001 --> 00:02:17,537
We didn't have time to prepare

28
00:02:18,204 --> 00:02:20,940
before we debuted as Sexy Zone.

29
00:02:24,410 --> 00:02:26,546
{\an8}<i>There was a sense of crisis as a group.</i>

30
00:02:32,519 --> 00:02:38,458
{\an8}<i>What's more, So Matsushima
went on medical hiatus.</i>

31
00:02:44,898 --> 00:02:46,232
{\an8}<i>And then...</i>

32
00:02:48,401 --> 00:02:51,471
{\an8}<i>the national tour scheduled
from March was postponed.</i>

33
00:02:54,007 --> 00:02:57,977
{\an8}<i>Each member worked to do what they could</i>

34
00:02:58,645 --> 00:03:02,415
{\an8}<i>in a struggle to break out
of their own shells.</i>

35
00:03:04,651 --> 00:03:05,552
{\an8}<i>On this day,</i>

36
00:03:05,618 --> 00:03:09,489
{\an8}<i>Fuma Kikuchi was recording
a variety program.</i>

37
00:03:09,556 --> 00:03:11,291
{\an8}-Could I get a comment?
-Yeah.

38
00:03:11,357 --> 00:03:12,692
For that long?

39
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:16,696
-It does say 16 minutes.
-That's amazing.

40
00:03:17,530 --> 00:03:20,700
I couldn't last 16 even if I shed blood.

41
00:03:21,701 --> 00:03:23,169
{\an8}<i>In 2008,</i>

42
00:03:23,236 --> 00:03:28,107
{\an8}<i>when he was a second year in junior high,
Kikuchi contacted the agency himself.</i>

43
00:03:30,543 --> 00:03:35,615
<i>He talks about his attractive image
which is the opposite of his personality.</i>

44
