I might be the most negative one.

45
00:03:41,955 --> 00:03:45,658
I think there is some frustration
with that, in the group.

46
00:03:46,159 --> 00:03:49,862
"Why is he so pessimistic?"
I think there's a bit of that.

47
00:03:51,264 --> 00:03:55,768
<i>That's why he's the one
who sees situations most calmly.</i>

48
00:03:56,636 --> 00:03:58,238
Five seconds. Four, three...

49
00:03:58,304 --> 00:04:04,410
<i>For him, the place where
he broke out of his shell was variety TV.</i>

50
00:04:06,646 --> 00:04:09,882
