When Mommy feeds me, it tastes so good!

73
00:05:55,021 --> 00:05:56,689
Rolling! Ready...

74
00:05:56,756 --> 00:05:59,025
<i>In the end, he gets slapped.</i>

75
00:05:59,092 --> 00:06:02,161
<i>He's taken a role that's different
from his usual image.</i>

76
00:06:04,731 --> 00:06:10,503
Things other people aren't doing
or that nobody has done before.

77
00:06:10,570 --> 00:06:14,707
I try it, and I think about it a lot.

78
00:06:18,344 --> 00:06:20,146
<i>His even features</i>

79
00:06:20,213 --> 00:06:23,516
<i>have earned him the name,
"Living National Treasure Face."</i>

80
00:06:27,553 --> 00:06:30,790
<i>He began a new series
in a women's fashion magazine.</i>

81
00:06:33,192 --> 00:06:36,496
<i>There was yet another member
trying new things.</i>

82
00:06:43,069 --> 00:06:47,874
{\an8}<i>The youngest of the group, Marius,
was searching for his own position.</i>

83
00:06:49,308 --> 00:06:50,576
Homework.

84
