I can't really show with Sexy Zone.

98
00:07:36,622 --> 00:07:37,990
I'm a little more...

99
00:07:38,057 --> 00:07:39,959
I can speak different languages.

100
00:07:40,026 --> 00:07:43,763
I do use that as a sort of weapon.

101
00:07:50,736 --> 00:07:52,305
{\an8}<i>Born in Germany,</i>

102
