129
00:09:13,653 --> 00:09:14,787
Alright!

130
00:09:14,854 --> 00:09:17,290
Next, we go up I think?

131
00:09:17,356 --> 00:09:20,826
We'll go up, and I have
a shoot with Ribon.

132
