Yes.

142
00:09:45,084 --> 00:09:46,619
Can we talk a bit?

143
00:09:46,686 --> 00:09:48,020
Yes, of course.

144
00:09:49,355 --> 00:09:54,226
<i>As the eldest,
Nakajima has always led the group.</i>

145
00:09:54,293 --> 00:09:57,330
My group is especially sensitive.

146
00:09:57,396 --> 00:10:00,199
A lot of them can be touchy.

147
00:10:00,266 --> 00:10:03,869
I just accept everything
without judgment.

148
00:10:03,936 --> 00:10:05,071
I think that's...

149
00:10:05,137 --> 00:10:09,342
a good quality and a bad one,
at least, in my opinion.

150
00:10:10,209 --> 00:10:15,548
<i>In 2008, Nakajima
auditioned at the agency on his own.</i>

151
00:10:17,383 --> 00:10:22,054
<i>There, he met Kikuchi,
who joined at the same time.</i>

152
00:10:23,155 --> 00:10:26,225
{\an8}<i>Ever since their Johnny's Jr. years,</i>

153
00:10:26,292 --> 00:10:30,329
{\an8}<i>they were popularly known as
the handsome duo "Fumaken."</i>

154
00:10:30,396 --> 00:10:33,633
{\an8}"FUMAKEN"

155
00:10:35,067 --> 00:10:38,571
<i>But as a result of their closeness...</i>

156
00:10:39,905 --> 00:10:44,176
We've been together for 12 years.

157
00:10:46,579 --> 00:10:48,614
There were times I hated him

158
00:10:49,115 --> 00:10:50,850
and times I liked him too.

159
00:10:50,916 --> 00:10:53,352
And also times I didn't care at all.

160
00:10:53,853 --> 00:10:57,156
But he's always been by my side.

161
00:11:02,595 --> 00:11:07,433
I guess we both have that awareness,
that it's a friendly competition.

162
00:11:08,968 --> 00:11:11,537
I think we both felt that strongly.

163
00:11:11,604 --> 00:11:13,506
So at one point...

164
00:11:14,340 --> 00:11:17,376
there was a time when it was all thorns.

165
00:11:18,044 --> 00:11:19,345
Yeah.

166
00:11:19,412 --> 00:11:23,282
Now that we're almost at
the tenth anniversary of our debut,

167
00:11:23,349 --> 00:11:26,118
we talked on the phone yesterday...

168
00:11:26,686 --> 00:11:28,254
Uh...

169
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:31,991
We had a meeting about a video
we're going to put online,

170
00:11:32,058 --> 00:11:34,493
so we talked about a lot of things.

171
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:38,564
He has this human side
that I want to show people.

172
00:11:38,631 --> 00:11:40,566
I think he should promote it more.

173
00:11:40,633 --> 00:11:43,502
In that sense, Kikuchi going on

174
00:11:43,569 --> 00:11:47,273
those prank shows,
variety shows and all that...

175
00:11:47,339 --> 00:11:51,877
I feel like he's on a good path right now.

176
00:11:52,845 --> 00:11:56,716
I really like how he isn't
trying to act all cool anymore.

177
00:11:59,285 --> 00:12:00,653
<i>According to Kikuchi...</i>

178
00:12:01,987 --> 00:12:05,691
I think Nakajima and I
are both a little odd.

179
00:12:06,258 --> 00:12:08,928
I do look at things from a step back.

180
00:12:08,994 --> 00:12:11,731
Or at least, I try to take a step back.

181
00:12:12,264 --> 00:12:14,533
So I think that might...

182
00:12:15,501 --> 00:12:18,504
sometimes look emotionally distant.

183
00:12:18,571 --> 00:12:21,073
Well, Nakajima is the eldest after all.

184
00:12:21,607 --> 00:12:23,442
I think he has his pride.

185
00:12:23,509 --> 00:12:26,946
He sometimes says so himself.

186
00:12:27,012 --> 00:12:29,982
But above all, Nakajima is more like...

187
00:12:31,383 --> 00:12:35,755
the point-getter.
He's really the shooter after all.

188
00:12:37,156 --> 00:12:41,393
So I have to give the assist.

189
00:12:41,460 --> 00:12:46,665
I feel like it's my job
to make those passes work.

190
00:12:46,732 --> 00:12:50,903
That's what I think.
It really feels like that.

191
00:12:51,937 --> 00:12:54,073
<i>Overcoming many barriers,</i>

192
00:12:54,140 --> 00:12:56,942
<i>the two grew to respect one another.</i>

193
00:12:58,544 --> 00:13:03,549
<i>Their readiness
to fight together is the same.</i>

194
00:13:06,085 --> 00:13:09,421
<i>And the member who acts
as the group's mediator.</i>

195
00:13:09,488 --> 00:13:12,491
<i>So Matsushima.</i>

196
00:13:14,894 --> 00:13:18,631
He's an adhesive,
but really more of a glue.

197
00:13:18,697 --> 00:13:20,900
As a member of Sexy Zone,

198
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:25,838
he's really like the sun.

199
00:13:25,905 --> 00:13:32,645
Just by being there,
the mood gets lighter.

200
