<i>Matsushima was
the mood maker for the group.</i>

212
00:14:09,181 --> 00:14:12,852
<i>As they hoped for his return from hiatus,</i>

213
00:14:13,452 --> 00:14:15,621
<i>the bandmates felt conflicted.</i>

214
