I really like So as a person,
and I respect him.

215
00:14:23,095 --> 00:14:24,897
I just want him to get better.

216
00:14:24,964 --> 00:14:30,035
And for example, if that means
he might not come back,

217
00:14:30,102 --> 00:14:32,271
If that's the case...

218
00:14:32,338 --> 00:14:37,643
If So is happy that way, then that's okay.

219
00:14:38,444 --> 00:14:40,079
I can't just say it.

220
00:14:41,113 --> 00:14:43,215
Of course it's better with five.

221
00:14:44,416 --> 00:14:48,554
I can't say, "Please, I want to perform
as five. Please come back."

222
00:14:49,889 --> 00:14:50,990
Yeah.

223
00:14:54,660 --> 00:14:55,928
I wish he could...

224
00:14:56,662 --> 00:14:59,365
somehow find a way to be happy.

225
00:14:59,865 --> 00:15:01,901
That's how I feel now I guess.

226
