239
00:15:58,757 --> 00:16:01,727
-We'd do our makeup together.
-Yeah, that's right.

240
00:16:02,761 --> 00:16:03,862
Good morning.

241
00:16:03,929 --> 00:16:04,897
Thanks.

242
00:16:04,964 --> 00:16:06,699
For what?

243
00:16:06,765 --> 00:16:07,666
What "thanks"?

244
00:16:07,733 --> 00:16:08,867
You did that for me.

245
00:16:08,934 --> 00:16:10,235
Of course I did!

246
00:16:10,769 --> 00:16:13,205
Wouldn't you say, "Long time no see?"

247
00:16:14,006 --> 00:16:15,941
We'd always message each other

248
00:16:16,008 --> 00:16:18,911
so it doesn't feel like
it's been a long time.

249
00:16:18,978 --> 00:16:21,380
In the sense of distance.

250
00:16:21,447 --> 00:16:22,982
It's scary while sleeping.

251
00:16:24,883 --> 00:16:27,753
<i>The same atmosphere as always.</i>

252
00:16:28,520 --> 00:16:31,991
<i>That's how they chose to respond.</i>

253
00:16:34,326 --> 00:16:35,194
You nervous?

254
00:16:35,260 --> 00:16:37,162
I'm super nervous.

255
00:16:37,663 --> 00:16:40,566
-I might pee my pants.
-Nothing's stopping you.

256
00:16:40,632 --> 00:16:42,201
Ah, the camera was on.

257
00:16:43,902 --> 00:16:45,304
Okay, rolling!

258
00:16:45,371 --> 00:16:47,873
Five seconds, four, three, two...

259
00:16:48,407 --> 00:16:49,942
Hello everyone.

260
00:16:50,009 --> 00:16:51,944
We are Sexy Zone!

261
00:16:52,011 --> 00:16:55,714
Today, we have some happy news.

262
00:16:55,781 --> 00:16:59,218
We wanted to tell you right away,
so we're making this video.

263
00:16:59,284 --> 00:17:00,652
-Yes.
-Everyone, well...

264
00:17:00,719 --> 00:17:03,155
-I know you already know.
-That's right.

265
00:17:03,222 --> 00:17:04,757
You've been waiting.

266
00:17:04,823 --> 00:17:07,659
-Yes, truly.
-Yes, I've been waiting.

267
00:17:07,726 --> 00:17:10,662
What shall we do? Should we call him?

268
00:17:10,729 --> 00:17:11,563
Or should we...

269
00:17:11,630 --> 00:17:13,432
What should we do?

270
00:17:13,499 --> 00:17:14,967
Wanna get him? Shori, go.

271
00:17:15,034 --> 00:17:17,136
-Okay, I'll go.
-You go.

272
00:17:17,636 --> 00:17:19,772
Hey, let's go.

273
00:17:19,838 --> 00:17:22,508
Yay!

274
00:17:22,574 --> 00:17:23,409
Woo!

275
00:17:23,475 --> 00:17:24,710
It's So!

276
00:17:24,777 --> 00:17:27,613
Yes. Sorry for being away for so long.

277
00:17:27,679 --> 00:17:29,715
I'm So Matsushima from Sexy Zone.

278
00:17:31,183 --> 00:17:33,819
It's public. You're coming back.

279
00:17:33,886 --> 00:17:36,021
Yes, thank you very much.

280
00:17:36,088 --> 00:17:37,689
Please support us!

281
00:17:37,756 --> 00:17:39,458
Please do!

282
00:17:39,525 --> 00:17:40,692
Do the honors.

283
00:17:40,759 --> 00:17:41,593
This has been...

284
00:17:41,660 --> 00:17:43,462
Sexy Zone!

285
00:17:43,529 --> 00:17:45,030
Yay!

286
00:17:45,097 --> 00:17:45,931
Sexy Zone!

287
00:17:47,266 --> 00:17:48,967
<i>And on this day,</i>

288
00:17:49,034 --> 00:17:52,938
<i>the shoot to announce
Matsushima's return ended.</i>

289
00:17:53,005 --> 00:17:55,474
It's been so long, I'm still sort of...

290
00:17:55,541 --> 00:17:57,209
Yeah, but it's still so...

291
00:17:57,276 --> 00:18:00,145
I feel like it's all coming back to me.

292
00:18:01,180 --> 00:18:02,147
Uh...

293
00:18:03,082 --> 00:18:07,553
{\an8}<i>Later, on the radio program he hosts,</i>

294
00:18:07,619 --> 00:18:09,254
{\an8}<i>Sato told the fans.</i>

295
00:18:10,122 --> 00:18:13,425
We have announced So Matsushima's return.

296
00:18:19,064 --> 00:18:23,202
We've caused everyone to worry
for nearly two years.

297
00:18:24,903 --> 00:18:29,441
We've always considered So
to naturally be a bandmate.

298
00:18:29,508 --> 00:18:31,043
So it's only natural.

299
00:18:31,110 --> 00:18:33,812
It's really just natural. Yeah.

300
00:18:34,580 --> 00:18:36,515
That's how much... Hmm.

301
00:18:37,683 --> 00:18:38,784
How can I put it?

302
00:18:39,585 --> 00:18:43,689
So that's why we say, "Welcome home."

303
00:18:43,755 --> 00:18:44,790
Yeah.

304
00:18:45,724 --> 00:18:50,696
Sexy Zone will go on to be
Sexy Zone in its true form.

305
00:18:50,762 --> 00:18:53,999
We'll show you
what Sexy Zone is all about.

306
00:18:54,066 --> 00:18:57,236
This was <i>Shori wo Kimi ni</i>
with Sexy Zone's Shori Sato.

307
00:18:59,304 --> 00:19:00,305
Good work.

308
00:19:00,372 --> 00:19:06,211
<i>Sato chose his words carefully
and shared his thoughts.</i>

309
00:19:08,981 --> 00:19:13,719
{\an8}<i>Soon after his return was the shoot
for the cover of their new song.</i>

310
00:19:15,921 --> 00:19:18,056
A photo shoot with the five of us is...

311
00:19:18,824 --> 00:19:21,059
Right? It's been a while.

312
00:19:21,126 --> 00:19:24,730
But it feels the same as always.
Just as it was before.

313
00:19:24,796 --> 00:19:27,666
I love how nothing has changed.

314
00:19:28,167 --> 00:19:29,568
We already discussed this!

315
00:19:29,635 --> 00:19:31,270
Why are you so excited?

316
00:19:31,336 --> 00:19:32,204
He's not excited.

317
00:19:32,271 --> 00:19:33,906
He's trying to make a good shot.

318
00:19:33,972 --> 00:19:36,341
We're setting up all these lights.

319
00:19:36,408 --> 00:19:37,643
Don't get in the way!

320
00:19:37,709 --> 00:19:39,178
-Shooting!
-Okay.

321
00:19:39,244 --> 00:19:40,345
They're shooting me.

322
00:19:40,412 --> 00:19:42,581
This feels so extravagant.

323
00:19:46,652 --> 00:19:50,355
This is Marius, I'm Matsushima.
We're SoMari!

324
00:19:54,826 --> 00:19:55,694
Well done today.

325
00:19:55,761 --> 00:19:57,062
Thank you.

326
00:19:57,763 --> 00:20:02,668
This was the first photo shoot
since I returned.

327
00:20:03,268 --> 00:20:06,271
I feel like it'll become
a special memory for me.

328
00:20:06,338 --> 00:20:10,642
A different kind of memory than usual.

329
00:20:11,143 --> 00:20:13,979
I hadn't worked with the four for a while

330
00:20:14,046 --> 00:20:17,082
and each of them had become
a little more mature.

331
00:20:17,149 --> 00:20:21,720
Their faces, too.
It was just refreshing to see.

332
00:20:21,787 --> 00:20:27,359
They really did keep Sexy Zone going,
that same environment.

333
00:20:27,426 --> 00:20:28,527
It's still there.

334
00:20:28,594 --> 00:20:32,431
And here I am, trying to
fit back into that, in the right way.

335
00:20:32,497 --> 00:20:35,133
At times like that, I listen to "RUN"

336
00:20:35,634 --> 00:20:39,171
as I work towards
the goals I set for myself...

337
00:20:39,238 --> 00:20:41,340
As I'm doing that,

338
00:20:41,940 --> 00:20:46,912
I can choose to see
negative things as positive.

339
00:20:46,979 --> 00:20:49,214
That's how this song speaks to me.

340
00:20:49,281 --> 00:20:52,084
And the four members
of Sexy Zone are singing it.

341
00:20:52,150 --> 00:20:54,720
That's the most important part.

342
00:20:54,786 --> 00:21:00,359
We're all doing our best
in the same circumstances.

343
00:21:00,425 --> 00:21:03,228
The fact that people I know are singing...

344
00:21:03,295 --> 00:21:05,931
That makes me really happy.

345
00:21:05,998 --> 00:21:09,434
Though that's probably something
other people can't feel.

346
00:21:10,869 --> 00:21:14,006
{\an8}<i>Next, the five appear on a music program.</i>

347
00:21:14,072 --> 00:21:15,440
{\an8}FIVE ONSTAGE AFTER 650 DAYS

348
00:21:17,276 --> 00:21:19,144
{\an8}<i>Fighting to catch up.</i>

349
00:21:20,479 --> 00:21:22,714
{\an8}I haven't been in front of cameras
in ages.

350
00:21:22,781 --> 00:21:25,851
{\an8}When I dance,
I get butterflies in my stomach.

351
00:21:26,451 --> 00:21:29,154
{\an8}<i>The bonds between the five...</i>

352
00:21:29,655 --> 00:21:33,625
{\an8}I wish So wouldn't worry.
He can tease, and criticize too.

353
00:21:33,692 --> 00:21:35,861
{\an8}I believe in him.

354
00:21:35,927 --> 00:21:39,631
{\an8}You don't need to be perfect.
You can just have fun.

355
00:21:39,698 --> 00:21:42,234
{\an8}I just want everyone
to look forward to it.

356
00:21:42,301 --> 00:21:45,170
{\an8}I'm sure Matsushima feels the same way.

357
00:21:45,237 --> 00:21:47,139
{\an8}-So this is B?
-It's the regular one.

358
00:21:47,205 --> 00:21:48,273
{\an8}It's not B?

359
00:21:48,340 --> 00:21:49,708
{\an8}Thank you everyone.

360
00:21:49,775 --> 00:21:52,611
{\an8}<i>They've only just begun.</i>

361
00:21:52,678 --> 00:21:54,980
